00:00:00.550 --> 00:00:02.760
Bu biz sizga bergan asl XML .

00:00:02.760 --> 00:00:05.510
U vertikal chiziqli layout edi.

00:00:05.510 --> 00:00:08.090
Va elementlar ham vertikal 
ustun bo‘ylab joylashgan edi.

00:00:08.090 --> 00:00:10.220
Topshiriqdagi mana bu rasmga ko‘ra, 

00:00:10.220 --> 00:00:14.930
biz elementlarni nisbiy layoutdan foydalangan holda 
ko‘proq ro‘yxat elementlariga o‘xshashini xohlaymiz.

00:00:14.930 --> 00:00:16.680
Mana bu yerda yechim berilgan.

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.460
Rasm chap tomonda va uchta matn ko‘rinishlari 

00:00:19.460 --> 00:00:22.020
o‘ng qo‘l tomonda bo‘lishi uchun 
biz joylashuv tartibini o‘zgartirdik.

00:00:22.020 --> 00:00:26.210
Bu joylashuv tartibini qurish maqasadida men 
ildiz view ni chiziqli layout qilmasdan 

00:00:26.210 --> 00:00:28.180
nisbiy layout qilib o‘zgartirdim.

00:00:28.180 --> 00:00:29.530
Bu ochilish tegi bo‘lganligi sababli, 

00:00:29.530 --> 00:00:32.700
men pastdagi yopilish tegini 
ham o‘zgartirishim kerak edi.

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:36.610
Ochilish va yopilish teglari orasida 
bizda to‘rtta farzand viewlari bor.

00:00:36.610 --> 00:00:40.200
Men yana vertical orientation attribute ni 
ham olib tashladim, 

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:42.580
chunki u chiziqli layoutga tegishli edi.

00:00:42.580 --> 00:00:46.240
Nisbiy layout uchun esa orientation attribute ning keragi yo‘q.

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:48.750
Rasm allaqachon to‘g‘ri joylashtirilgan edi.

00:00:48.750 --> 00:00:52.400
Nisbiy layoutning birinchi farzandi 
har doim avtomatik ravishda 

00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:53.270
yuqori chap burchakka joylashtiriladi.

00:00:53.270 --> 00:00:57.440
Va mana bu biz elementlar ro‘yxati uchun biz 
xohlagan narsa, demak, u bir xilda qoladi.

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:59.720
Keyingisida bizda Pebble Beach 
deb yozilgan TextView bor.

00:01:00.730 --> 00:01:04.410
Biz bu TextView ni ImageView ning o‘ng tomoniga 
joylashtirishni xohlaymiz, demak, biz 

00:01:04.410 --> 00:01:10.180
 layout_torightof attribute ini qo‘shishimiz kerak 
va undan keyin rasm view ga ishorani ham.

00:01:10.180 --> 00:01:13.800
 ImageView ga ishora qilish uchun 
biz ImageView ga ID atributini 

00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:15.400
qo‘shishimiz kerak edi.

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:19.100
Men shunchaki uni photo deb nomladim, ammo siz 
o‘zingiz xohlagan biron narsa deb nomlashingiz mumkin.

00:01:19.100 --> 00:01:22.260
Bu to‘g‘ri joylashtirilgan rasm va 
birinchi TextView .

00:01:22.260 --> 00:01:25.740
Keyingi TextView California 
matnini ko‘rsatish uchun.

00:01:25.740 --> 00:01:29.498
 California TextView rasmning o‘ng 
tomoniga joylashtirilishi kerak 

00:01:29.498 --> 00:01:32.110
va Pebble Beach TextView ning pastida bo‘lishi kerak.

00:01:32.110 --> 00:01:35.510
Demak, birinchi biz layout_toRightof 
atributni qo‘shamiz va

00:01:35.510 --> 00:01:36.890
rasmga ishora qilamiz.

00:01:36.890 --> 00:01:39.620
Undan so‘ng biz pastdan yana boshqa bir 
layout atributini qo‘shamiz va 

00:01:39.620 --> 00:01:41.880
keyin biz birinchi TextView ga ishora qilamiz.

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:46.860
Bu birinchi TextView uchun ID ham qo‘shish talab 
qilinadi, biz shunchaki o‘zining nomi bilan nomlaymiz.

00:01:46.860 --> 00:01:50.060
Ajoyib, demak, joylashdi, 
 ImageView va ikkita TextView .

00:01:50.060 --> 00:01:53.622
Nihoyat, bizda 10 mil uzoqlikdagi masofani 
ko‘rsatib turuvchi TextView bor.

00:01:53.622 --> 00:01:55.420
U rasmning o‘ng tarafiga va California matn 

00:01:55.420 --> 00:01:56.890
 view sining pastiga joylashtirilgan.

00:01:57.900 --> 00:02:01.370
Shunday qilib, biz layout_toRightof atributini rasmga 
ishora qilishi uchun qo‘shishimiz kerak edi,

00:02:01.370 --> 00:02:05.730
va biz yana pastdagi layout uchun ham 
bitta atribut qo‘shishimiz kerak edi,

00:02:05.730 --> 00:02:09.008
va undan keyin TextView ning 
joylashuvi uchun ishora ham.

00:02:09.008 --> 00:02:13.280
Bu manzil TextView siga ham 
ID qo‘shishni talab etadi.

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:15.960
Men shuningdek, masofa TextView siga ham ID qo‘shdim.

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:18.030
Hattoki biz unga hech qayerda ishora 
qilmayotganimizga qaramasdan, 

00:02:18.030 --> 00:02:20.340
bironta view ga ID 
qo‘shish zarar qilmaydi.

00:02:20.340 --> 00:02:23.560
Mobodo siz unga keyinroq ishora qilmoqchi 
bo‘lsangiz u doimo o‘sha yerda turadi.

